set-bg: img/map_2.jpg
new-page: true
go-to: start_2

@start_2
title: Example
new-page: true

This is a game of alternate history. Despite being the modification of the semi realistic base game, modification itself allows exploration of nearly-impossible things through *dynamic* mechanics of the game without the elements of make-it-believe or realism lite. 

- @1928_easy: Begin (Easy difficulty)
- @1928_main: Begin (Normal difficulty)
- @1928_hard: Begin (Hard difficulty)
- @1928_historical: Begin (Historical mode)
- @challenge: Challenges and Conditions

@challenge

Choose your challenges!

> *Spartacist Victory: [? if spartac_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if spartac_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*
> *Inverted World: [? if inverted_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if inverted_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*
> *Gang: [? if gang_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if gang_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*
> *Modern Democracy: [? if dem_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if dem_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*
> *New Party: [? if new_partei_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if new_partei_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*
> *Agrarian Revolution: [? if peasant_revolution = 1: ON ?][? if peasant_revolution != 1: OFF ?]*
> *Camarillamulator: [? if cmr_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if cmr_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*
> *Vanilla: [? if vn_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if vn_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*
> *Dice: [? if dice_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if dice_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*
> *Duel: [? if duel_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if duel_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*
> *Hindenburg: [? if hindenburg_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if hindenburg_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*
> *FPTH: [? if fptp_variable = 1: ON ?] [? if fptp_variable = 0: OFF ?]*
> *Base Gamemode Trust Me: [? if april_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if april_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*

- @spartacus: Spartacist Victory!
# - @inverted: Randomize relationships!
- @gang: All of the gang is here! 
- @democracy: Democracy simulator, extremists are banned.
- @new: SPD is newly formed party.
- @bauern: Agrarian Revolution
- @camarilla: Camarillamulator
- @hindenburg: Hindenburg is not.
- @duel: Duel gamemode.
- @vanilla: Vanilla-esque gamemode.
- @dice: Dice Gamemode
- @fptp: First Past the Hell
- @modern: 5% threshold. Alr
- @april: Vanilla Superesque Normal Gamemode of First of Fourth.
- @start_2: Back

@modern

Do you love being thresholded by 4.8% like BSW did? alr.

- @mo_2: True
- @mo_3: False
- @challenge: Back.

