@camarilla

= Camarillamulator

Camarilla is formed at the beginning of the game, mind controlling Hindenburg. Can you all somehow oust his ass?

- @cmr_2: True
- @cmr_3: False
- @challenge: Back.

@cmr_2
view-if: cmr_challenge = 0
on-arrival: cmr_challenge = 1
go-to: camarilla

Turned on!

@cmr_3
view-if: cmr_challenge = 1
on-arrival: cmr_challenge = 0
go-to: camarilla

Turned off!


@inverted

= Inverted World

The political compass has been flipped! Prepare for the doomsday politics!

- @inverted_2: True
- @inverted_3: False
- @challenge: Back.

@inverted_2
view-if: inverted_challenge = 0
on-arrival: inverted_challenge = 1
go-to: inverted

Turned on!

@inverted_3
view-if: inverted_challenge = 1
on-arrival: inverted_challenge = 0
go-to: inverted

Turned off!

@bauern

= Agrarian Revolution

Demographics only consist of dominating rurals, some workers, some merchants and unemployed. Good luck.

- @bauern_2: True
- @bauern_3: False
- @challenge: Back.

@bauern_2
view-if: peasant_revolution = 0
on-arrival: peasant_revolution = 1
go-to: bauern

Turned on!

@bauern_3
view-if: peasant_revolution = 1
on-arrival: peasant_revolution = 0
go-to: bauern

Turned off!

@new

= New Party

SPD is newly formed party of the small unions and some social democrats. Can you make it prosper?

